cn: 1、简历信息不同，但姓名、手机号、出生年月、电子邮箱四个条件任三个相同，系统便判断为同一人
en: 1. The system will recognize individuals with different info., but same name, telephone, birth date and email on resumes as the same one.

cn: 2、系统识别出同一人后会保留时间最近的一份简历，其他自动标注失效状态，筛重后再次投递该职位的同一人简历自动为”失效“状态
en: 2. The system will save the lastest resume when recognizing the same person, and mark failure state for other resumes from this person automatically. Ater screening, if this person delivered to this position again, his/her resume would be marked as failure state automaticlly.
